<chapter xml:id="geogebra">
  <title>Geogebra for GCT</title>
  <introduction>
  	<p>
      Geogebra offers dynamic compass and ruler constructions on-line.  We use this program often in our investigations.  Indeed much of the key developments in the text rely on compass and ruler constructions, and to understand them we need to get in and work with them.
    </p>

